title: Query Retrieve View
description: निर्दिष्ट करता है behavior on Rejection Note Stored

title: Show Instances Rejected By Code
description: Indicates if the Q/R Services shall show instances rejected by the specified code इस फॉर्मेट में (CV, CSD, 'CM'')

title: Hide Rejection Note With Code
description: Indicates if the Q/R Services shall hide Rejection Notes with the specified code इस फॉर्मेट में (CV, CSD, 'CM'')

title: Hide Not Rejected Instances
description: Indicates if the Q/R Services shall hide instances not rejected by any reason.
